Class ListViewPdfPrintAction

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.guidewire.pl.web.print.process.PrintGenerator, com.guidewire.pl.web.print.process.XslGenerator

    public final class ListViewPdfPrintAction
extends ListViewPrintAction
    A ListViewPrintAction for list views that only support PDF output. This is useful for list views like NotesLV with unconventionally-formatted columns that can't be readily exported to CSV.
